review_blob:
Very nice steam!
A moderate malty taste, Fruity complexety combined with a nice bitterhop, leaving a long lasting brown lager taste on the back of the tongue.

This IPA appears dark brown, with a very complex body. High ammount off roasted flavour, topped by a rich taste off roasted malt and even a bit off oak at the end of the taste. Its longlasting, with a nice semithick foam.
